KCCN-FM (100.3 MHz "FM100") is a Hawaiian contemporary hit radio station. The SummitMedia outlet broadcasts with ERP of 100kW. The station's studios are located in Downtown Honolulu and its transmitter is located near Akupu. It also transmits on Oceanic Spectrum digital channel 852 for the entire state of Hawaii.
